<span class="pageheading">10 Questions to Ask a Home Inspector</span><br><br>


<ol class="text">
 <li class="text">What
     are your qualifications? Are you a member of the American Association of
     Home Inspectors?<br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![endif]></li>
 <li class="text">Do you
     have a current license? Inspectors are not required to be licensed in
     every state.<br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![endif]></li>
 <li class="text">How
     many inspections of properties such as this do you do each year?<br
     style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![endif]></li>
 <li class="text">Do you
     have a list of past clients I can contact?<br style='mso-special-character:
     line-break'>
     <![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![endif]></li>
 <li class="text">Do you
     carry professional errors and omission insurance? May I have a copy of the
     policy?<br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![endif]></li>
 <li class="text">Do you
     provide any guarantees of your work?<br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![endif]></li>
 <li class="text">What
     specifically will the inspection cover?<br style='mso-special-character:
     line-break'>
     <![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![endif]></li>
 <li class="text">What
     type of report will I receive after the inspection?<br style='mso-special-character:
     line-break'>
     <![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![endif]></li>
 <li class="text">How
     long will the inspection take and how long will it take to receive the
     report?<br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>
     <![endif]></li>
 <li class="text">How
     much will the inspection cost?</li>
</ol>


